originalText.text: Our experience with Liability Insurance was excellent!! They provided exceptional customer service and took the time to educate and discuss our options. originalText.text: I needed to find tattoo artist insurance and decided to get a quote online just to see; I was contacted the same day by the insurance broker with all the information I needed to make an informed decision. He called me within a few hours, going over every detail with me step by step and answering every question I had. He was patient with my lack of knowledge in this field and extremely helpful! He also secured a fantastic rate! The entire process was much faster and easier than I had anticipated! Thank you once more!
